朋友、Gay佬、雞蟲同賭徒<br />\n笑下屌下咪算<br />\n有心做實事點會睇連登9UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ac8221dca37eb9b38b6b22ea4eef2fd843a1a6","tid":1895703,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"從來都要獨立思考㗎啦，人哋講嘅嘢要自己過濾下先，再唔係就自己親身去試下再判斷。咁樣先會真係篩到真&middot;高質黃店。"},{"pid":"b66c56ca09f927736a1128159bce15f1d1b28949","tid":1895703,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:46:43.000Z","msg":"講得啱呀"},{"pid":"8b35cdb1e99df6ca5bb877aa119ac9995519a7b7","tid":1895703,"uid":152431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:52:15.000Z","msg":"根本冇得universally define咩叫黃 <br />\n個圈係點其實係你自己定 唔係人地幫你定 <br />\n你有ABC標準 我有CDE標準 當明知龍門周圍都係嘅時候 <br />\n其實拗埋咩偽黃與否係一啲營養都冇 點都唔會有結論<br />\n反正我放張whatsapp圖就會有人on99幫我share出去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n汰弱留強其實係必然 笑到最後嘅舖頭/生意一定係個venn diagram intersect到最多嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Branden_Fitelson/publication/255588575/figure/fig4/AS:669562756419598@1536647609629/Venn-diagram-visualization-of-a-3-event-probability-space-O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FBranden_Fitelson%2Fpublication%2F255588575%2Ffigure%2Ffig4%2FAS%3A669562756419598%401536647609629%2FVenn-diagram-visualization-of-a-3-event-probability-space-O.png&h=81a26b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有個最主要嘅問題就係驚輸驚失敗 所以有部分人本能反應唔肯接受現實 亦可以稱為玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27d521acb57f230c691460e7e2c92543033d422","tid":1895703,"uid":152431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738f9666b3eb48f4390e1ebdfda246b3f7367211","tid":1895703,"uid":210009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T16:53:28.000Z","msg":"預左比人負評<br />\n繼續圍爐取暖唔正視問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後問人係唔係唔支持黃色經濟圈<br />\n講真如果好似光榮咁又平又大份又好食<br />\n邊度有咁多不滿？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:54:26.000Z","msg":"唔好食嘅唔會食<br />\n唔啱食嘅唔會食<br />\n你個侍應閪嘅就更加唔使諗<br />\n家下唔係冇得揀我做咩要揀食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45855c02759fbcf17d8c7b05c63bf0d555d00a0","tid":1895703,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"根本唔使理佢扮唔扮黃，總之當哂係黃宣傳佢黃到金佢想變翻藍都唔撚得啦"},{"pid":"e15149f861b53c9abe8deaba56240775e43d6ed0","tid":1895703,"uid":34757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d4921c699f2d5aea904cdc9c1c4ddeb0978d4c8","tid":1895703,"uid":275351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"又回到14年，做D不知所謂野攪散左個運動。<br />\n有無想起死去架手捉呀<br />\n你日日訓得好安心喇<br />\n佢佢無去探你地咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef221cf51b22ecc1a67c3d30596261a5b9cbc712","tid":1895703,"uid":152431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e15149f861b53c9abe8deaba56240775e43d6ed0","tid":1895703,"uid":34757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:59:11.000Z","msg":"好簡單嘅其實 get a fucking life<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要某堆life loser每一日嘅生存目的唔係上呢度拎認同感嘅話 我肯定會好好多"},{"pid":"494c40ceffbf58132ad77311976789c07a43c905","tid":1895703,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:00:26.000Z","msg":"第一點好難define<br />\n<br />\n我真係識有啲老闆本身2014年係屌人佔中<br />\n6月大遊行佢覺得係搞事<br />\n但721之後醒覺, 經過831直頭二轉埋<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得不如直接啲<br />\n店門肯貼張紙, &quot;不招待警員及其家屬&quot;<br />\n而家肯定唔係藍店"},{"pid":"e5296abb8f798dc4c65efd67cb92cc8b37f3cc18","tid":1895703,"uid":279763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/